<section xmlns:ns0="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" containing-doc="D.C. Code">
  <num>4-405</num>
  <heading>Schedule of payments by parents.</heading>
  <para>
    <num>(a)</num>
    <text>Parents who receive day care services pursuant to § <cite path="§4-404">4-404</cite> [repealed] shall pay a portion of services according to the sliding scale set forth in subsection (b) of this section.</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(b)</num>
    <text>
      <table>
        <tr>
          <th>Increment</th>
          <th>Adjusted Income</th>
          <th>Parent Fee (Percent of Child Care Paid by Parent)</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>1</td>
          <td>Under $8,020</td>
          <td>Flat Fee of $2 per week</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>2</td>
          <td>$8,020–$9,012</td>
          <td>5%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>3</td>
          <td>$9,013–$10,005</td>
          <td>10%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>4</td>
          <td>$10,006–$10,998</td>
          <td>15%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>5</td>
          <td>$10,999–$11,991</td>
          <td>20%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>6</td>
          <td>$11,992–$12,984</td>
          <td>25%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>7</td>
          <td>$12,985–$13,977</td>
          <td>30%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>8</td>
          <td>$13,978–$14,970</td>
          <td>35%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>9</td>
          <td>$14,971–$15,963</td>
          <td>40%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>10</td>
          <td>$15,964–$16,956</td>
          <td>45%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>11</td>
          <td>$16,957–$17,949</td>
          <td>50%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>12</td>
          <td>$17,950–$18,942</td>
          <td>55%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>13</td>
          <td>$18,943–$19,935</td>
          <td>60%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>14</td>
          <td>$19,936–$20,928</td>
          <td>65%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>15</td>
          <td>$20,929–$21,921</td>
          <td>70%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>16 Over</td>
          <td>$21,921</td>
          <td>100%</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(c)</num>
    <text>The fee schedule shall be effective April 1, 1990. The Mayor may revise the fee schedule by rule.</text>
  </para>
